  <fr:mainmatter>
    <fr:blockquote>My main interests at the moment are type theory, including Homotopy Type Theory, and its applications to higher category theory. I am currently looking at various definitions of globular higher categories and am thinking about semi-strictness problems and types of composition.</fr:blockquote>
  </fr:mainmatter>
